OL,3,CIsraeli settlers grow bolder in West
OL,4,CBank with world distracted by war in
OL,5,CIran
OL,7,FWith the world's attention focused on
OL,8,Fthe Iran War, settlers have
OL,9,Fintensified their offensive, as ITV
OL,10,FNews Senior International
OL,11,FCorrespondent John Irvine reports
OL,13,FThe video footage chronicles a
OL,14,Fshocking new low when it comes to
OL,15,FIsraeli settler attacks on the
OL,16,FPalestinians of the West Bank.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
