OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1778054737
OL,3,CIsraeli settlers grow bolder in West
OL,4,CBank with world distracted by war in
OL,5,CIran
OL,7,FThe man, who is wearing an Israeli
OL,8,Farmy uniform, is filmed taking careful
OL,9,Faim with a rifle and firing several
OL,10,Fshots towards the village of Al-
OL,11,FMughayyir.
OL,13,FThe gunfire is being directed at the
OL,14,Fvillage school, where pupils either
OL,15,Ftry to take cover or run away.
OL,17,FAmong those who the teachers try to
OL,18,Fevacuate is 14-year-old Aws al-Naasan.
OL,19,FBut just after he runs out of the
OL,20,Fschool gate, he is shot in the head.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
