OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1778054737
OL,3,CIsraeli settlers grow bolder in West
OL,4,CBank with world distracted by war in
OL,5,CIran
OL,7,FThe footage shows some of his
OL,8,Fschoolmates shouting his name and then
OL,9,Frushing towards him as he lies on the
OL,10,Fground immobile.
OL,12,FAs they try to tend to him, you can
OL,13,Fsee a puff of dust as another bullet
OL,14,Fstrikes the school wall.
OL,16,FA teacher, Waheed Abu Alya, is another
OL,17,Fof those who attempts to help the
OL,18,Fteenage victim.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
