OL,3,CIsraeli settlers grow bolder in West
OL,4,CBank with world distracted by war in
OL,5,CIran
OL,7,FHe told a cameraman working for ITV
OL,8,FNews that before the shooting, he
OL,9,Fapproached a group of settlers,
OL,10,Fincluding the killer, and tried to
OL,11,Freason with them and persuade them to
OL,12,Fback off.
OL,14,FHe said they told him to go away or
OL,15,Fthey would shoot him.
OL,17,FTragically, as he ran to the scene,
OL,18,FWaheed's brother, Jihad Abu Naim, was
OL,19,Fshot and killed by the settler
OL,20,Fwielding the rifle. A parent at the
OL,21,Fschool, Mr Abu Naim was aged 32.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
