OL,7,FIn response to our request for an
OL,8,Fupdate on any repercussions regarding
OL,9,Fthe double shooting, the Israel
OL,10,FDefence Forces (IDF) referred us to a
OL,11,Fprevious statement in which they said
OL,12,Fa review was underway, the findings of
OL,13,Fwhich would be sent to the relevant
OL,14,Fauthorities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
