OL,7,FDuring a UN Security Council meeting
OL,8,Fon the Middle East this week, the UK
OL,9,Fambassador said that while the Israeli
OL,10,Fgovernment had rightly condemned the
OL,11,Fdouble killing, accountability for
OL,12,Fprevious incidents had been severely
OL,13,Flacking.
OL,15,FWith the world's attention focused on
OL,16,Fthe Iran War, settlers have
OL,17,Fintensified their offensive.
