OL,3,CIsraeli settlers grow bolder in West
OL,4,CBank with world distracted by war in
OL,5,CIran
OL,7,FOver the course of the 59 days since
OL,8,Fthe war began, there have been 378
OL,9,Fseparate incidents, according to one
OL,10,Fhuman rights group.
OL,12,FAs was the case with most schools on
OL,13,Fthe West Bank, the war meant the
OL,14,Fclosure of the girls' school in the
OL,15,Fvillage of Umm al Khair.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
