OL,3,CIsraeli settlers grow bolder in West
OL,4,CBank with world distracted by war in
OL,5,CIran
OL,7,FEarlier this month, when the school re-
OL,8,Fopened, dozens of pupils found their
OL,9,Fway to it blocked by barbed wire,
OL,10,Fwhich villagers said had been put in
OL,11,Fplace by Israelis from a nearby
OL,12,Fsettlement.
OL,14,FThe villagers accuse the settlers of
OL,15,Ftrying to take over Palestinian land
OL,16,Fso they can expand the settlement.
