OL,5,CIran
OL,7,FThe UK's Foreign Secretary Yvette
OL,8,FCooper has condemned Israel's approval
OL,9,Fof the death penalty for Palestinians
OL,10,Fwho murder Israelis.
OL,12,FA video filmed on April 13 shows
OL,13,Fschoolgirls sitting and standing by
OL,14,Fthe newly erected fence. Villagers say
OL,15,Fthat Israeli soldiers later fired
OL,16,Fteargas and smoke can be seen in the
OL,17,Ffootage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
