OL,3,CIsraeli settlers grow bolder in West
OL,4,CBank with world distracted by war in
OL,5,CIran
OL,7,FAccording to the United Nations, 1,750
OL,8,FPalestinians have been displaced by
OL,9,Fsettler violence or faced access
OL,10,Frestrictions so far this year.
OL,12,FHuman rights groups say that Israeli
OL,13,Fsecurity forces ignore, enable or
OL,14,Fencourage the settler attacks.
OL,16,FArrests are rare and convictions ever
OL,17,Frarer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
